physical relationships of the sound without any grid to constrain it.", "tokens": [50365, 1900, 4001, 6159, 295, 264, 1626, 1553, 604, 10748, 281, 1817, 7146, 309, 13, 50590], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.16939018549544088, "compression_ratio": 1.5477178423236515, "no_speech_prob": 3.491237680897097e-12}, {"id": 45, "seek": 19072, "start": 195.22, "end": 200.06, "text": " To hear that math, the format uses a synthesis system called the Rise Engine.", "tokens": [50590, 1407, 1568, 300, 5221, 11, 264, 7877, 4960, 257, 30252, 1185, 1219, 264, 34482, 7659, 13, 50832], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.16939018549544088, "compression_ratio": 1.5477178423236515, "no_speech_prob": 3.491237680897097e-12}, {"id": 46, "seek": 19072, "start": 200.06, "end": 205.9, "text": " This engine takes those dehydrated formulas and rehydrates them, synthesizing a perfect audio", "tokens": [50832, 639, 2848, 2516, 729, 32102, 5468, 30546, 293, 319, 21591, 12507, 552, 11, 26617, 3319, 257, 2176, 6278, 51124], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.16939018549544088, "compression_ratio": 1.5477178423236515, "no_speech_prob": 3.491237680897097e-12}, {"id": 47, "seek": 19072, "start": 205.9, "end": 207.98, "text": " wave in real time.", "tokens": [51124, 5772, 294, 957, 565, 13, 51228], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.16939018549544088, "compression_ratio": 1.5477178423236515, "no_speech_prob": 3.491237680897097e-12}, {"id": 48, "seek": 19072, "start": 207.98, "end": 215.56, "text": " Stored as mathematical relationships, the performance can be rendered at any resolution\u201496 kHz, 192 kHz,", "tokens": [51228, 745, 2769, 382, 18894, 6159, 11, 264, 3389, 393, 312, 28748, 412, 604, 8669, 2958, 22962, 350, 21409, 11, 1294, 17, 350, 21409, 11, 51607], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.16939018549544088, "compression_ratio": 1.5477178423236515, "no_speech_prob": 3.491237680897097e-12}, {"id": 49, "seek": 21556, "start": 215.56, "end": 219.22, "text": " or a massive 768 kHz 